John Davey (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Davey_(actor) 0 John Davey is a retired American actor. He is best known for portraying Captain Marvel on the Shazam! television series in the mid-1970s after Jackson Bostwick was dismissed in the early part of the second season.
